<span id="freeTextContainer9403048605013856003">I swear this is like an American Shakespearean tragedy and I love it. I love how the tension builds and how it evetually explodes. Miller makes you somehow hate Eddie but also pity and root for him at the same time, or is that just me? Also a brilliant insight into the life of Italian immigrants in NY at the time too. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


